msgstr "``live_price_acquire_freq``"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "拉价频率，如 `15MIN`"
msgstr "Price increase frequency, such as `15MIN`"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "与策略步频不协调时可能缺数据"
msgstr "Data may be missing when the pace of the strategy is not coordinated."

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:45
msgid ""
"以下键**非启动硬性门槛**，但强烈建议确认——它们影响最小成交单位、日志落盘与磁盘"
"占用。与上表同属 `qt.configure` 范围，可在同一脚本里一并写入。"
msgstr ""
"The following keys are **not hard requirements for startup**, but it is "
"strongly recommended to confirm them—they affect the minimum transaction "
"unit, log writes to disk, and disk usage. They belong to the `qt.configure` "
"scope along with the table above and can be written to the same script."

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:47
msgid ""
"**如何使用**：若成交数量「对不齐整手」或日志找不到文件，回头查本表对应行。"
msgstr ""
"**How to use:** If the transaction quantity is not \"in complete lots\" or "
"the log file cannot be found, go back and check the corresponding row in this "
"table."

