#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:184
msgid "7.1 Dashboard 与 interactive 模式"
msgstr "7.1 Dashboard and Interactive Mode"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:186
msgid ""
"Trader Shell 启动后默认进入 **dashboard 模式**：单行状态区滚动显示下一任务倒计"
"时、监视列表实时价与系统消息，无需输入命令即可观察运行节奏。需要手动下单、查配"
"置或执行运维命令时，按 **Ctrl+C** 打开模式选单，或在 interactive（命令）模式下"
"输入 **`dashboard`** 返回 dashboard。"
msgstr ""
"Trader Shell starts in **dashboard mode** by default: a single-line status "
"area scrolls to display the countdown to the next task, real-time prices in "
"the monitoring list, and system messages, allowing you to observe the "
"operational rhythm without entering commands. To manually place orders, check "
"configurations, or execute maintenance commands, press **Ctrl+C** to open the "
"mode menu, or type **`dashboard`** in interactive (command) mode to return to "
"the dashboard."

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "模式"
msgstr "Mode"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "行为"
msgstr "Behavior"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "**dashboard**"
msgstr "**dashboard**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "自动刷新状态行与监视价；Trader 主循环在后台继续运行"
msgstr ""
"The status row and monitored price are automatically refreshed; the Trader "
"main loop continues to run in the background."

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "**interactive（命令）**"
msgstr "**interactive (command)**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md
msgid "传统 `Cmd` 提示符，可输入 `buy`、`config`、`artifacts` 等命令"
msgstr ""
"The traditional `Cmd` prompt allows you to enter commands such as `buy`, "
"`config`, and `artifacts`."

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:193
msgid "**Ctrl+C 模式选单（dashboard 或命令模式下均可用）**"
msgstr ""
"**Ctrl+C mode selection menu (available in both dashboard and command mode)**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:195
msgid ""
"在 **5 秒**内按 **1** → 进入命令模式；**2** → 回到 dashboard；**3** → 退出并停"
"止 Trader"
msgstr ""
"Within **5 seconds**, press **1** → to enter command mode; **2** → to return "
"to the dashboard; **3** → to exit and stop Trader."

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:196
msgid "**无需按 Enter**，数字键立即生效"
msgstr "**No need to press Enter, the number keys take effect immediately.**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:197
msgid "**5 秒内无输入** → 自动恢复中断前的模式"
msgstr ""
"**No input within 5 seconds** → Automatically resume the mode before the "
"interruption."

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:198
msgid "**选单等待期间再次按 Ctrl+C** → 立即退出（与选 **3** 等效）"
msgstr ""
"**Press Ctrl+C again during the menu wait time** → Exit immediately "
"(equivalent to selecting **3**)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md:200
msgid ""
"若主循环发生未预期异常，Shell 会提示按 **1** 回到 dashboard 或 **3** 退出；"
"**5 秒无输入**时默认回到 dashboard，Trader 继续运行。"
msgstr ""
"If an unexpected exception occurs in the main loop, the Shell will prompt you "
"to press **1** to return to the dashboard or **3** to exit; if there is no "
"input for **5 seconds**, it will return to the dashboard by default, and the "
"Trader will continue running."

